title: 396. Andy, Hany Rambod & DJ CTI: PayPal Offering Bribes, Video Games Could Trigger Heart Attacks & Agency Offered Steele $1 Million To Corroborate
itunes:title: 396. Andy, Hany Rambod & DJ CTI: PayPal Offering Bribes, Video Games Could Trigger Heart Attacks & Agency Offered Steele $1 Million To Corroborate
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ are joined in the studio by 20x Olympia-winning coach and Evogen Nutrition CEO Hany Rambod. They discuss PayPal offering bribes of $15 to stop people from canceling accounts, video games potentially triggering heart attacks in children, and a senior agency analysts reporting that the bureau offered Christopher Steele $1 million to corroborate the dossier.
